rows.label: qst1003105_msg001
rows.name:
Helped out all three
distribution centers, did you?

rows.label: qst1003105_msg003
rows.name:
The Invidian folks were really under
pressure there. They were ready to
turn nasty on those refugees.

rows.label: qst1003105_msg004
rows.name:
It ain't right, but compassion
starts to seem like a luxury
when people get desperate.

rows.label: qst1003105_msg005
rows.name:
We're all guilty of it. If you can't
look after yourself, you start to
think you can't help others.

rows.label: qst1003105_msg006
rows.name:
But thanks to you, we've got the
wherewithal to not be so selfish.

rows.label: qst1003105_msg007
rows.name:
This will make everyone's
lives a whole lot easier.

rows.label: qst1003105_msg008
rows.name: Thanks for all your help, guys!
